data.description: This impressive 5 acre hill country estate is nestled in the in the heart of Waggener Ranch.  The ranch doubles as an exotic wildlife reserve that features Axis and Fallow Deer, Aoudad Sheep and Blackbuck Antelope. Horses are also permitted.  206 Dry Bear Creek  is an entertainer's dream.  This magnificently appointed property boasts a full wet-bar, a high-tech theatre complete with surround sound, multiple TVs, and space to accommodate various seating and furniture arrangements. The chef's kitchen is equipped with Thermador appliances built in espresso machine and a plethora of storage options. The spacious owners suite is illuminated by a wall of windows and is accompanied by a luxurious bath with his & her water closets.  After working out in your fully equipped gym, and shooting hoops on your custom-built basketball court, enjoy a dip in the enormous pool or soak those tired muscles in a hot tub that fits all of your friends and family.
